snippet.title: Amber Laura Heard | Birthday | Celebration Party
snippet.description:
Amber Laura Heard is an American actress.  After playing a character role in TV and movies, Heard has her first role in the horror film ' All the boy love Mandy lane'.
____________________________________________

Born: April 22, 1986 (age 35 years), Austin, Texas, United States

Height: 1.7 m

TV shows: The Stand, Criminal Minds, The Playboy Club, The O.C., Overhaulin', more

Upcoming movie: Aquaman 2
